SUMMARY:Draw Outdoors with Jeff Hagen
DESCRIPTION:Whether you‚Äôre an experienced artist or looking to build your confidence in art, Jeff Hagen is here to guide you in this inspiring outdoor drawing workshop! Join him Sunday, May 17, from 12:30‚Äì3:30 PM at Brown County State Park.\n\nWith over 30 years of experience, Hagen will help you develop skills in perspective, contour, and observational drawing techniques. Take in the beauty of nature as you observe, connect, and create in a relaxed, supportive environment.\nParticipants should bring a folding chair and sketchbook. All other supplies and lunch will be provided.\nRegistration is $150. To sign up or learn more, contact Jeff Hagen at jeffhagenart@gmail.com or call (812) 929-5798.\n\n
