DESCRIPTION:Celebrate Indiana‚Äôs rich artistic legacy at the 48th Annual Indiana Heritage Arts Exhibition & Sale at the Brown County Art Gallery. One of the Midwest‚Äôs premier juried art exhibitions, this longtime tradition showcases outstanding works from talented Indiana artists inspired by the heritage and beauty of the Brown County Art Colony. Visitors can explore a stunning collection of paintings and fine art spanning impressionism, landscapes, still lifes, and more‚Äîall available for viewing and purchase throughout the exhibition. Whether you‚Äôre an avid collector, passionate art lover, or simply looking to experience Brown County‚Äôs vibrant creative spirit, this celebrated annual event offers an unforgettable look into Indiana‚Äôs artistic tradition.\n
