SUMMARY:Summer Goat Camp
DESCRIPTION:\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCampers will spend their days at our 46-acre goat and chicken sanctuary in Brown County, Indiana. Kids will have the opportunity to interact with our 118 goats and 80 chickens by learning about and participating in ‚Äòmorning chores‚Äô, socializing with the goats in playing and petting sessions (which the goats love), and having the chance to meet some of the people who help make the Sanctuary run day to day.\nAdditionally, our property will be theirs to explore (with supervision). With all of the abundant wildlife and diverse flora and fauna that southern Indiana has to offer, kids will have many opportunities to connect with and learn from nature through hikes, crafts and other activities.\n\n\n\n\n\n\nDates: June 15-19 Monday-Friday\nTime: 9:00am to 4:00pm\nAges: 8-12 yrs\nClick to register\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nPricing\n$390.00 per camper*\n*Includes a daily plant-based lunch and snack\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nHealth & Safety\nWe are first and foremost an animal sanctuary and take the health and safety of our visitors and residents very seriously. If you would like to read more about this, please download our Health & Safety Policies.\n\n\n\n\n\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/summer-goat-camp/
