SUMMARY:Cask & Still Social
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an unforgettable evening at the distillery as we host our Cask & Still Social‚Äîan intimate night celebrating exceptional whiskey, incredible food, and great company.\nThis exclusive experience will feature tastings of standout Hard Truth spirits, including our Amburana Blend Straight Bourbon and Double Oaked Rye, thoughtfully paired with expertly crafted small bites. The evening‚Äôs culinary offerings will be led by celebrity chef Dave White of Great White Smoke, serving bold, whiskey‚Äëfriendly flavors designed to complement each pour.\nGuests will also enjoy a curated tasting experience highlighting limited and specialty offerings from Hard Truth, showcasing the craftsmanship and innovation behind our distilling process.\nTicket holders will have the opportunity to purchase featured spirits and select limited‚Äërelease whiskeys, some of which are available only at the distillery.\nConsider this evening a taste of what‚Äôs ahead as we build toward our Bourbon & BBQ Festival on July 18‚Äîa refined, behind‚Äëthe‚Äëscenes preview for true whiskey and barbecue lovers.\nRaise a glass, savor the craftsmanship, and experience Hard Truth like never before.\n
