SUMMARY:Smoke School With Dave White
DESCRIPTION:\nKick off the season of Bourbon and BBQ¬Ý with an unforgettable evening of smoke, flavor, and bourbon at Hard Truth Distilling Co. Join Dave White, Pit Master of Great White Smoke, for a 90‚Äëminute celebrity¬Ýcooking¬Ýdemonstration that takes you step‚Äëby‚Äëstep through the art of crafting a perfectly smoked pork butt.\n\n\n\nDuring this immersive demo, Dave will walk guests through his smoking process, share expert tips, and bring BBQ techniques to life all while you enjoy a delicious meal inspired by the demonstration. Each guest will experience a guided tasting of our whiskey and receive a goodie bag with more information.\n\n\n\nWhether you‚Äôre a seasoned pit master, a backyard BBQ enthusiast, or looking for a memorable weekend experience, this event dishes up great food, great company, and a laid‚Äëback atmosphere at the distillery.\n\n\n\nCome hungry. Leave inspired.\n\n
