SUMMARY:The Brown County Art Guild Presents: Art In the Garden ‚Äì Countryside Blooms & Brushes 2026
DESCRIPTION:Experience the beauty of Art in the Garden ‚Äì Countryside Blooms & Brushes!¬Ý¬Ý\nAn unforgettable annual evening awaits in the heart of Brown County. Join the Guild Artist Members as they paint¬Ýen¬Ýplein air, capturing the beauty of the countryside & spring flowers in real time. Wander the Austin Historic Farm, savor delicious food & relax to the sounds of live music. Original artwork¬Ý& pottery¬Ýwill be available for purchase.¬Ý¬ÝIt‚Äôs¬Ýa celebration of art, nature, and community!¬Ý¬Ý¬Ý¬Ý\n¬Ý\nSaturday,¬ÝMay 30, 2026¬Ý\nJenny &¬ÝBill Austin‚Äôs Country Retreat¬Ý¬Ý\n$100 per person¬Ý¬Ý\n5 ‚Äì 8 pm¬Ý¬Ý\nLive Music¬Ý\nHeavy hors d‚Äôoeuvres by Nashville House Catering¬Ý& Cash Bar¬Ý\nGuild Artist¬ÝDemonstrations¬Ý¬Ý\nPaintings¬Ý& Pottery¬Ýfor Sale¬Ý¬Ý\nParking on Site¬Ý¬Ý\nRain or Shine¬Ý¬Ý\nPurchase¬Ýtickets¬Ýin person at the Guild,¬Ýcall 812-988-6185 or¬Ýonline at:¬Ý\nhttps://browncountyartguild.org/event/art-in-the-garden-countryside-blooms-brushes/¬Ý\n______________________________________________________________________¬Ý\n¬Ý\nBrown County Art Guild¬Ý‚Äì A not for profit organization¬Ýlocated¬Ýin the heart of downtown Nashville, Indiana.¬Ý¬ÝOn display throughout its galleries is a prized collection of historic paintings as well as current works for sale from regional award-winning member artists.¬Ý¬Ý\n¬ÝAlso offered throughout the year are artist demonstrations, workshops, and special exhibits.¬Ý¬Ý¬Ý\n¬ÝGallery hours March through December 2026, Monday ‚Äì Saturday, 11 ‚Äì 5 and Sunday, 12 ‚Äì 4 or by appointment.¬Ý\nIf you would like more information, call 812.988.6185 or visit our web site¬Ýhttps://browncountyartguild.org/¬Ý\n
