SUMMARY:New Exhibitions at the Brown County Art Guild!
DESCRIPTION:March 20 ‚Äì¬ÝJuly¬Ý17,¬Ý2026¬Ý\nGuild¬ÝArtist¬ÝExhibition and Sale¬Ý\nSpring brings renewal, creativity, and fresh inspiration. Join us for the Guild Artist Exhibition & Sale¬Ýshowcasing¬Ýnew works from our Guild Artist Members. Experience the beauty of the season through painting, color, and artistic expression.¬Ý\n¬Ý\n¬Ý\nMarch 20¬Ý‚Äì¬ÝJuly 17, 2026¬Ý\nNature‚Äôs Symphony¬Ý\nSpecial Exhibition & Sale¬Ý\nDiscover¬ÝNature‚Äôs Symphony¬Ý‚Äì¬ÝSpecial¬ÝExhibition¬Ý& Sale¬Ýfeaturing artwork by our talented Guild Artists. Experience how each artist interprets the beauty, rhythm, and movement of nature‚Äîcapturing the harmony of landscapes, light, color, and season in their own unique voice.¬Ý\n\nBrown County Art Guild¬Ý‚Äì A not for profit organization¬Ýlocated¬Ýin the heart of downtown Nashville, Indiana.¬Ý¬ÝOn display throughout its galleries is a prized collection of historic paintings as well as current works for sale from regional award-winning member artists.¬Ý¬ÝThe Guild also offers artist demonstrations, workshops,¬Ýand a variety of¬Ýevents¬Ýand¬Ýprograms¬Ýthroughout the year.¬Ý¬Ý¬Ý\nMarch¬Ý‚Äì¬ÝDecember: Monday‚ÄìSaturday, 11 ‚Äì 5 and Sunday, 12 ‚Äì 4¬Ý¬Ý\nWINTER HOURS:¬ÝJanuary ‚Äì February: Thursday ‚Äì Saturday 11 ‚Äì 5¬Ýand Sunday 12-4 or by appointment.¬Ý\nFor more¬Ýinformation,¬Ýplease call the Guild at 812-988-6185 or visit our website:¬Ýhttps://browncountyartguild.org/¬Ý\n
