DESCRIPTION:Charlene Marsh Studio and Gallery Memorial Weekend Open House\nMay 22-25, 2026\nFriday, Saturday, and Monday, 10 a.m. ‚Äì 5 p.m., Sunday 1 ‚Äì 5 p.m. EST.\nFeaturing:¬Ý\n\nAll works are available for purchase during the 4 day, open house, holiday weekend (cash, checks, & credit cards accepted).\nThe opportunity to acquire one-of-a-kind, oil paintings from the new collection, ‚ÄúSpirit of Compassion‚Äù .\nCarefully curated selection of notable, original, plein air, forest paintings.\nYoga mats with sacred geometry designs (limited quantity).\nTapestries, limited number available and no more will ever be made.\nLimited Edition Fine Art Prints.\nAll works are available for purchase after May 25, 2026 by appointment only.\nDrinks and vegetarian refeshments provided to guests.¬Ý\nTour organic, flower and vegetable gardens.\nBask in the transformational power of the healing forest.\nLet nature, art, and the forest wrap you in beauty, peace, calm, and joy.\nRare peek to see where the artist takes inspiration creating the artworks.\n\nCharlene Marsh Studio and Gallery\n\n4013 Lanam Ridge Road\n\nNashville, Indiana 47448\n\nStudio/Gallery:¬Ý 812-988-4497\n\nCell/Text:¬Ý 812-371-6750\n\nEmail:¬Ý Char@CharleneMarsh.com\n\n\n
