SUMMARY:Alice in Wonderland Jr
DESCRIPTION:\n\nDisney‚Äôs Alice in Wonderland JR. is a vibrant, family-friendly musical adaptation of the classic Disney film and Lewis Carroll‚Äôs beloved stories. Follow young Alice as she falls down the rabbit hole into the whimsical world of Wonderland, where she meets iconic characters like the White Rabbit, Cheshire Cat, Mad Hatter, and Queen of Hearts. Filled with beloved songs like ‚ÄúThe Unbirthday Song‚Äù and ‚ÄúPainting the Roses Red,‚Äù plus new music inspired by the 2010 film, this 60-minute stage show celebrates imagination, adventure, and fun for all ages.\n\n\n\n\nOur next summer camp is coming up in June 2026, registration is open!\n\n\nRegistration packets are available at the high school front desk.\n\n\n
