SUMMARY:War in the Woods
DESCRIPTION:¬ÝGet ready for one of the wildest, most adrenaline-charged drag-racing events in the country ‚Äî War in the Woods No Prep, held at Brown County Dragway in Morgantown, Indiana. Twice each year, the speed-obsessed and the curious come together for a full throttle weekend of no-prep racing action and high-stakes competition. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+2Brown County Indiana+2\nüìÖ Upcoming Dates (2026):\n\n\nMay 29‚Äì30\n\n\nSeptember 18‚Äì19 war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nüìç Location:Brown County Dragway ‚Äî 480 Gatesville Road, Morgantown, IN 46160 Brown County Indiana+1\nWhat to Expect:\n\n\n‚ö° High-octane drag races across multiple classes like Small Tire, Big Tire, Hard Tire, Stick Shift, Nitroous Mayhem and more. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nüîä Drivers meetings, chip draws, and a track that goes ‚Äúhot‚Äù at 3:00 p.m. both days ‚Äî expect action and intensity from start to finish. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nüöó A raw ‚Äúno prep‚Äù setup for daring street cars, where traction is minimal and every run is a gamble ‚Äî it‚Äôs what makes War in the Woods the wildest in the sport. No Prep Racing+1\n\n\nüéüÔ∏è General admission tickets available at the gate (cash only): $25 for one-day or $40 for a two-day pass. VIP packages (when available) offer perks like premium parking, food/drink vouchers, and exclusive access. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nImportant for Spectators:\n\n\nBring a chair ‚Äî spectator seating is limited and mostly standing or informal. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nNo overnight camping or motorized spectator vehicles allowed ‚Äî plan accordingly. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\nParking is assigned on arrival; please follow staff directions ‚Äî blocking driveways or track access will result in towing. war-in-the-woods-no-prep.com+1\n\n\n
URL:https://browncounty.com/events/warn-in-the-woods/
