SUMMARY:Fall Nature Retreat: Nature Journaling
DESCRIPTION:Immerse yourself in the beauty of fall at Waycross during our Fall Nature Journaling Retreat. The vibrant colors of the changing seasons will provide the perfect backdrop for deep observation and creativity. This weekend retreat will offer a peaceful space to connect with the natural world, using art and journaling as tools to deepen your awareness of nature in the season of fall. Guided prompts, outdoor sketching sessions, and time spent exploring the colorful fall foliage will foster a deeper connection with nature and creation.\n\n\nOctober 2-4, 2026\n\n\nCheck-in: 4-6pm\n\n\nCheck-out: 10am\n\n\n\n\nAll ages welcome, minors must be accompanied by an adult.\n\n\nProgram Rates\n\n\nAttendance cost is calculated during online registration, depending on your lodging selection. Rates are per person and include program fees, lodging and meals.\n\n\nConference Center ‚Äì Single Occupancy: $350 per person\n\n\nConference Center ‚Äì Double Occupancy: $280 per person\n\n\nYouth (10-17): $150 per person\n\n\nChildren (4-9): $110 per person\n\n\n3 and under: $0\n\n\n\n\n\n\n
