SUMMARY:All Y‚Äôall Come to Camp
DESCRIPTION:Spend the weekend surrounded by nature, with classic camp activities like campfires, worship, games, and outdoor adventures ‚Äì plus plenty of time to relax and unwind at your own pace. Whether you want to dive into all the action or simply enjoy the peaceful setting, this weekend is yours to enjoy.\nJoin us for a refreshing weekend filled with fun, adventure and community. Waycross staff will lead a variety of activities, and participants are encouraged to take part as much or as little as they like.\n\n\nSeptember 4-6, 2026\n\n\nCheck-in: 4-6pm\n\n\nCheck-out: 1pm\n\n\n\n\nAll ages welcome, minors must be accompanied by an adult.\n\n\nProgram Rates\n\n\nAttendance cost is calculated during online registration, depending on your lodging selection. Rates are per person and include program fees, lodging and meals.\n\n\nConference Center ‚Äì Single Occupancy: $400 per person\n\n\nConference Center ‚Äì Double Occupancy: $330 per person\n\n\nMain House/Sleeping Wing ‚Äì Multi-Occupancy: $260 per person\n\n\nCabins ‚Äì Multi-Occupancy (adult): $180 per person\n\n\nYouth 10-17: $200 per person\n\n\nChildren 4-9: $160 per person\n\n\n3 and under: $0\n\n\n\n\n\n\n
